65AC2832.Line38.D5161: Wanderer, I'm sorry, we've no time for thanks. Meet us in Dahlgur, when you can.

81F960FB.VoiceDir34.D5161: Can't get up. Pain. Frustration. Fear.

97CEBBAC.Line32.D5161: Bloody demons... if they set them on Dahlgur--!

CBACC36C.Line36.BC41C: It's all right, I’ll carry you back to camp, get you to the healer.
